Job Description
Share
As a Spa Receptionist you are responsible to coordinate with the Spa team on the daily operation of the department, delivering a high standard of guest interaction and customer service, whereby your role will include but not be limited to the below responsibilities;•	Coordinate and communicate with the Spa team to ensure a smooth operation•	Ensure all Spa standards are followed when dealing with guests •	Ensure all Spa standards are following when making appointments and recording information•	Maintain up to date knowledge of all treatments offered and products sold / used•	Ensure Spa operation follows SOP guidelines and regulations•	Ensure all Reception areas are clean, re-stocked and set up as per the Spa standard•	Maintain the privacy of all guests ensuring that no details of the guest are disclosed•	Assist in the control of stock and inventory for all retail products•	Prepare all end of day and monthly reports•	Ensure that all payments received are managed as per the Spa standard•	Manage all communication with guests by email•	Report all guest complaints / queries to Management immediately
Keyword: SPA Receptionist
